---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "LG Dishwasher Repair | Southern California | QuadWash, TrueSteam";
const description = "LG dishwasher repair across Southern California, QuadWash, TrueSteam, TrueDry, ThinQ Wi-Fi, LDT / LDF families. Korean engineering. $89 diagnostic waived. (424) 325-0520.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/lg-dishwasher-repair/";

const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Is the LG LinearCompressor class action relevant to dishwashers or just refrigerators?",
    a: "Refrigerators only. The 2020 class-action settlement covering LG refrigerators manufactured January 2014 through December 2017 with Linear Compressor defects is a refrigerator-specific matter, it doesn't apply to LG dishwashers, which use entirely different wash and drain-pump architecture. LG dishwashers have a separate reliability profile: the QuadWash rotating-arm system, Direct Drive motor architecture, and TrueSteam generator have their own maintenance and failure patterns distinct from refrigerator compressor issues. Our techs approach LG dishwasher service with platform-specific knowledge, wash-arm bearings, spray nozzle clogging, Direct Drive motor service, steam-generator scale. If you have both an LG fridge and an LG dishwasher, they're service-path-separate: the fridge might qualify for Linear Compressor 10-year parts warranty if under 10 years old, but the dishwasher is entirely its own service category."
  },
  {
    q: "What LG dishwasher models are most common in LA?",
    a: "By volume, LG LDT and LDF families dominate LA LG dishwasher service, 24-inch built-in configurations with QuadWash four-spray-arm system, TrueSteam generator on higher trims, TrueDry fan-assisted drying, ThinQ Wi-Fi connectivity on current-generation units. LDT5678, LDT7808, LDF5545, LDP6797 are common model-family call-outs we see across LA condos and mid-market kitchens, Koreatown, Sherman Oaks, Van Nuys, Pasadena, Long Beach, Irvine volume-heavy. SignatureCare panel-ready LDF configurations show up in mid-premium kitchen remodels where cabinetry integration matters. LG's top-control layouts (hidden controls on door top) are more common than front-control on current generations. Less common: LG compact 18-inch dishwashers (not a major LG product in US market, Bosch Ascenta and Beko dominate compact)."
  },
  {
    q: "Our LG dishwasher isn't drying dishes, is that the TrueDry system failing?",
    a: "Possibly, and the diagnostic splits by which drying system your LG uses. Higher-trim LG dishwashers use TrueDry with a fan-assisted drying cycle; mid-trim uses condensation drying enhanced by the stainless-steel interior's heat retention. Dry-failure diagnostic order: (1) rinse aid, LG drying performance (like most dishwashers) is highly rinse-aid-dependent; verify rinse aid is being dispensed and the dispenser isn't empty; $89 diagnostic if this is the fix; (2) TrueDry fan motor (higher trim only), failure presents as dishes coming out wet despite correct rinse aid use; fan swap $280–$440; (3) heating element, on models that use heat-assist drying (some LG variants), element failure affects dry cycle; element $260–$420; (4) stuck vent door / vent flap mechanism, flap stays closed during drying, moisture can't escape; $180–$280 mechanism service; (5) control-board dry-cycle logic fault, rare; $380–$580 board swap. Our techs verify rinse-aid and vent-flap function first, the fix is often cheaper than customers expect."
  },
  {
    q: "QuadWash vs 3-arm wash, is QuadWash actually better for service?",
    a: "QuadWash uses four spray arms (two rotating arms plus a Multi-Motion spray system with additional directional spray jets) vs. conventional dishwasher three-arm or two-arm setups. For wash performance, QuadWash delivers genuinely better coverage on oddly-shaped loads, sheet pans, tall water bottles, French-door-fridge-style casserole dishes. For service, more spray arms mean more potential wear points: four arms means four sets of spray-nozzle clog risks and four bearings to eventually wear. Spray arm cleaning + nozzle unclogging is more involved on QuadWash than simpler systems ($120–$220 service vs. $80–$160 on 2-arm), but individual arm replacement runs similar ranges to other brands ($140–$260 per arm). Overall LG dishwasher service economics are competitive with Samsung and mid-premium Bosch 500 Series."
  },
  {
    q: "LG dishwasher showing error code, which ones are common?",
    a: "LG's error-code display (on the control panel LED or via ThinQ app notification) maps to specific fault categories. Most common codes we diagnose: <b>AE</b> (anti-flood / leak detected), AquaStop-equivalent has tripped; source-trace the leak before clearing (inlet valve gasket, sump, door seal, pump housing); leak repair $180–$380 depending on location. <b>IE</b> (inlet / water supply), dishwasher not receiving water; inlet valve swap $240–$380 or supply-line troubleshoot. <b>OE</b> (outlet / drain), drain not clearing; filter clean or drain pump service $89–$280. <b>HE</b> (heater), heating element not reaching temperature; element swap $260–$420. <b>FE</b> (fill overflow), fill beyond set point; pressure switch or inlet valve stuck open; $220–$340. Our techs carry LG-code reference in dispatch, helps triage by phone before site visit."
  },
  {
    q: "What does LG dishwasher repair cost in LA?",
    a: "Residential diagnostic is $89, waived when you authorize the repair. Common LG bands: drain filter clean $89 (often free at diagnostic); drain pump $220–$340; inlet valve $240–$380; door latch + switch $200–$320; door gasket $220–$360; heating element $260–$420; TrueDry fan motor (higher trim) $280–$440; QuadWash spray arm replacement $140–$260; QuadWash nozzle unclog service $120–$220; control board $380–$580; ThinQ Wi-Fi module (rare, reconfiguration usually sufficient) $180–$280; Direct Drive motor (rare full replacement) $420–$620; steam generator (TrueSteam higher trim) $360–$520. LG parts through LG USA distribution (3-7 day typical common items, 5-10 day specialty). First-visit repair rate strong on common service items; control-board and Direct Drive motor are second-visit completion."
  }
];

const schemaJsons = [
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "LocalBusiness", "@id": canonical + "#business",
    "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair, LG Dishwasher Service",
    "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/same-day-appliance-repair.png",
    "url": canonical, "telephone": MAIN_PHONE_TEL, "priceRange": "$$",
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ]
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "serviceType": "LG Dishwasher Repair",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ],
    "description": "LG dishwasher repair across Southern California, LA, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, Riverside. LDT and LDF families, QuadWash four-spray-arm, TrueSteam generator, TrueDry fan-assisted drying, ThinQ Wi-Fi. Korean-engineering platform distinct from refrigerator Linear Compressor context. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "priceSpecification": { "@type": "PriceSpecification", "price": "89.00", "priceCurrency": "USD", "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair" } }
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a } }))
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "LG", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/lg/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "LG Dishwasher Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">
    {schemaJsons.map((schema) => (<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />))}
  </Fragment>

  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>LG dishwasher not cleaning or drying? Same-day service across LA:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › LG › Dishwasher Repair</div>
    <h1>LG Dishwasher Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      LG Electronics is one of the top three residential dishwasher brands in the US by volume alongside
      Samsung and Bosch. The Korean-conglomerate parent (LG Electronics, Seoul) drove mass-market share
      through the 2010s via the QuadWash four-spray-arm wash system, TrueSteam generator, TrueDry
      fan-assisted drying, and ThinQ Wi-Fi connectivity. Our techs see LG concentrated across our
      service area in condo markets (Koreatown / Hollywood / DTLA apartment buildings on the LA side,
      Garden Grove / Buena Park / Fullerton along the OC Korean-American corridor, plus Long Beach
      and Newport Beach high-rises), Valley mid-market kitchens (Sherman Oaks / Van Nuys / Northridge),
      Pasadena and South Bay volume, growing Westside mid-market presence, OC mainstream households
      (Anaheim, Santa Ana, Tustin, Irvine), Ventura mid-market (Oxnard, Ventura, Simi Valley,
      Camarillo), and the Inland Empire family-housing belt (Ontario, Rancho Cucamonga, Riverside,
      Fontana, Murrieta). Platform-separate from
      LG refrigerator Linear Compressor service context, different engineering, different parts, different
      diagnostic. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta"><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div>
    <ul class="hero-facts">
      <li><b>Top-3 volume brand across SoCal</b>, deep LG parts inventory through LG USA distribution</li>
      <li><b>QuadWash + TrueSteam + TrueDry</b>, LG-signature feature stack on current generation</li>
      <li><b>ThinQ Wi-Fi ecosystem</b>, app reconfig often resolves connectivity issues (no parts)</li>
      <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b>, waived when you authorize the repair</li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar"><div class="wrap"><span>BHGS #A49573 · Insured</span>
    <span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span><span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>LG across Southern California, Korean-engineering dishwasher platform, mass-market volume</h2>
    <p>LG Electronics entered the US residential dishwasher market in the 2000s and grew to top-three volume status by the mid-2010s through aggressive feature development, QuadWash, TrueSteam, TrueDry, ThinQ, at price points below the German luxury tier (Miele / Bosch 800 Series) but above mass-market budget brands. Our installed base concentrates in volume geographies across all five counties: Koreatown / Hollywood / Downtown LA and the Garden Grove / Fullerton OC Koreatown corridor (where the Korean-American demographic drives LG brand recognition), Valley mid-market kitchens across Sherman Oaks / Van Nuys / Northridge / Woodland Hills, Pasadena / San Gabriel Valley / South Bay suburban mid-market, central OC mainstream (Anaheim, Santa Ana, Irvine, Tustin), Ventura mid-market (Oxnard, Ventura, Simi Valley), and the Inland Empire family-housing corridor (Ontario, Rancho Cucamonga, Riverside, Fontana, Murrieta).</p>
    <p>Higher-trim InstaView-equivalent aesthetic + Craft-Ice analogs on LG refrigeration don't transfer directly to the dishwasher line, LG dishwashers are focused on wash and dry performance with ThinQ connectivity as the cross-appliance ecosystem layer. Our techs service full LG dishwasher lineup across our 8 service territories with Korean-platform-specific diagnostic knowledge. Related: <a href="/brands/lg-refrigerator-repair/">LG refrigerator repair</a> covers the refrigerator-specific Linear Compressor service context separately; platforms don't cross-reference.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>LG dishwasher failures our techs see most often</h2>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Won't drain, filter and drain pump</h3><p>Drain filter clean often resolves at diagnostic ($89); drain pump replacement $220–$340 when pump mechanical fault confirmed. OE error code on panel indicates drain-side fault.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Dishes coming out wet, TrueDry fan or rinse aid</h3><p>Rinse-aid dispenser check first ($89 diagnostic if that's the fix), then TrueDry fan motor on higher trim ($280–$440), then vent-flap mechanism ($180–$280).</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>QuadWash spray arm service</h3><p>Spray nozzle clogging at 3-5 year intervals on Southern California hard-water households (worst in IE); clean + descale $120–$220. Individual arm replacement $140–$260 when bearing wear is root cause. Four-arm architecture means checking all four during service.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>TrueSteam generator scale on higher-trim units</h3><p>TrueSteam steam generator on higher-trim LDT and LDF families develops scale from SoCal hard water, particularly fast in the Inland Empire (Rancho Cucamonga, Temecula). Descaling + component check $260–$380; steam generator replacement $360–$520 when descaling doesn't restore function.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Direct Drive motor fault on 8-plus-year units</h3><p>LG's Direct Drive motor architecture is long-service-life but occasionally fails at 8-10 years. Motor swap $420–$620; diagnostic requires distinguishing Direct Drive motor fault from simpler pump-and-motor faults common on other brands.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>ThinQ Wi-Fi disconnection</h3><p>Usually network-side, not hardware. Router reconfig, 2.4GHz vs 5GHz clarification, ThinQ app re-pair. $89 diagnostic visit typically sufficient. Wi-Fi module actual failure rare ($180–$280 swap when needed).</p></div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>LG dishwasher product lines we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LDT series (mainstream volume)</h3><p>LDT5678, LDT7808 and related 24-inch built-in families with QuadWash, TrueDry, ThinQ. Mass-market kitchen volume across all 5 counties.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LDF series</h3><p>LDF5545, LDF6797 families. Top-control layout, panel-ready options, TrueSteam on higher trim.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>SignatureCare panel-ready</h3><p>Integrated panel-ready configurations for kitchen remodels requiring flush-to-cabinet install.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>QuadWash four-spray-arm</h3><p>LG-signature wash system with Multi-Motion spray jets plus two rotating arms. Service-path includes all four arms.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>TrueSteam generator (higher trim)</h3><p>Steam generator service requires LA-hard-water descaling + specialty parts.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>ThinQ Wi-Fi + SmartThings integration</h3><p>Network-side reconfiguration service for most ThinQ connectivity calls.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>LG vs Samsung, the Korean-brand dishwasher comparison</h2>
    <p>Two Korean conglomerates compete for overlapping mid-market / mid-premium share.</p>
    <p><b>LG</b>, QuadWash four-arm wash, TrueSteam, TrueDry, Direct Drive motor, ThinQ Wi-Fi. Stronger on wash-coverage pitch. This page.</p>
    <p><b>Samsung</b>, WaterWall single-arm sweeping wash, StormWash, Zone Booster, AutoRelease Door, SmartThings. Stronger on dry-performance and feature-count pitch. See <a href="/brands/samsung-dishwasher-repair/">Samsung dishwasher repair</a>.</p>
    <p>Both platforms have comparable service economics. Parts networks roughly equal depth in LA. Choice often comes down to kitchen ecosystem (ThinQ vs SmartThings household) and specific wash-performance preference.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>What LG dishwasher repair costs in LA</h2>
    <table class="price-table">
      <tr><th>Service</th><th>Typical Range</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Residential diagnostic</td><td>$89</td><td>Waived with repair</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Drain filter clean</td><td>$89</td><td>Often free at diagnostic</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Drain pump replacement</td><td>$220 – $340</td><td>OE code fault</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Inlet valve</td><td>$240 – $380</td><td>IE code</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door latch + switch</td><td>$200 – $320</td><td>Daily-use wear</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door gasket</td><td>$220 – $360</td><td>6-8 year service</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Heating element</td><td>$260 – $420</td><td>HE code</td></tr>
      <tr><td>TrueDry fan motor</td><td>$280 – $440</td><td>Higher trim only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>QuadWash spray arm replacement</td><td>$140 – $260</td><td>Per arm</td></tr>
      <tr><td>QuadWash nozzle clean / descale</td><td>$120 – $220</td><td>Preventive</td></tr>
      <tr><td>TrueSteam descaling</td><td>$260 – $380</td><td>SoCal hard water (esp. IE)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>TrueSteam generator replacement</td><td>$360 – $520</td><td>When descaling insufficient</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Control board</td><td>$380 – $580</td><td>Electronic generations</td></tr>
      <tr><td>ThinQ Wi-Fi module</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>Reconfig usually sufficient</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Direct Drive motor</td><td>$420 – $620</td><td>Rare 8-plus-year failure</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Broader reference: <a href="/price-list/dishwasher-repair-cost/">dishwasher repair cost guide</a> · <a href="/price-list/dishwasher-door-spring-repair-cost/">door spring service</a>. Related: <a href="/brands/samsung-dishwasher-repair/">Samsung dishwasher repair</a> · <a href="/brands/lg-refrigerator-repair/">LG refrigerator repair</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Service areas, where our LG calls come from</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>Koreatown + Central LA</h4><p>Koreatown · Hollywood · Mid-Wilshire · <a href="/west-hollywood/">West Hollywood</a> · <a href="/downtown/">Downtown LA</a></p></div>
      <div><h4>San Fernando Valley</h4><p>Sherman Oaks · Van Nuys · Northridge · Woodland Hills · <a href="/encino/">Encino</a> · Reseda</p></div>
      <div><h4>Pasadena + San Gabriel Valley</h4><p><a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena</a> · Alhambra · Monterey Park · Arcadia</p></div>
      <div><h4>South Bay + Long Beach</h4><p>Torrance · Long Beach · Redondo Beach · Carson · Hawthorne</p></div>
      <div><h4>Westside mid-market</h4><p>Culver City · Mar Vista · Palms · <a href="/santa-monica/">Santa Monica</a> · Westwood</p></div>
      <div><h4>OC mainstream + Koreatown corridor</h4><p>Anaheim · Santa Ana · Garden Grove · Fullerton · <a href="/irvine/">Irvine</a> · Tustin · Buena Park</p></div>
      <div><h4>Ventura mid-market</h4><p><a href="/thousand-oaks/">Thousand Oaks</a> · Oxnard · Ventura · Simi Valley · Camarillo</p></div>
      <div><h4>Inland Empire family housing</h4><p>Ontario · <a href="/rancho-cucamonga/">Rancho Cucamonga</a> · Riverside · Fontana · Murrieta</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Related LG and dishwasher pages</h2>
    <ul class="related-links">
      <li><a href="/brands/lg-refrigerator-repair/">LG refrigerator repair →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/samsung-dishwasher-repair/">Samsung dishwasher repair →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/bosch-dishwasher-repair/">Bosch dishwasher repair →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/brands/signature-kitchen-suite-refrigerator-repair/">SKS refrigerator repair (LG luxury) →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/services/dishwasher-repair/">Dishwasher repair (service hub) →</a></li>
      <li><a href="/price-list/dishwasher-repair-cost/">Dishwasher repair cost guide →</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>LG dishwasher repair, frequently asked</h2>
    {faqs.map(f => (<details class="faq"><summary>{f.q}</summary><p set:html={f.a}></p></details>))}
  </div></section>

  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>LG dishwasher down? Call the branch closest to your home.</h2>
    <p>Same-day appliance repair across Los Angeles, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside counties. Residential diagnostic $89, waived with repair.</p>
  </div></section>
  <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="float-call" aria-label="Call now">☎ Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a>
</Layout>

<style>
